author: doogie
msg: OFBIZ-6270: This class used to be a javacc-based grammer for parsing
json; this method of json integration has been removed, in favor of
base/lang/JSON.  However, some external projects still use this legacy
form of json parsing.  So, this class implements the old api, but users
will get a deprecation warning when compiling against it.
